title: Ep - 12 - Tom Schwartz from Vanderpump Rules
description:
Kate speaks with Tom Schwartz from Vanderpump Rules about the show, his wedding, and what he predicts the rest of the cast will be doing in three years and also speaks with Sam Chasse about the premiere episode of Sister Wives.
